[The "Consultant" Diagnostic Support System for Veterinary Medicine lists 41 differential diagnoses involving porcines with fever and serous nasal discharge. In case human disease is observed in conjunction with the current pig mortality, the list becomes significantly shorter. Results of the undertaken investigation are anticipated with interest. - Mod.AS

